			<div class="content" id="post-content-3796395">
									

<p>Well I think in this case it's the idea that he never had to learn anything that we have developed in the three millenia since he last trained or really practice what he already knew, but has relied on his supernatural abilities instead. Which seems both clever and plausible to me.</p>
<p>Of course a good tactical shooter probably would have the same advantages, but that's really a conceit of this tale that he is able to have contempt for firearms.</p>

